Connor Davis
Homework 3: Lighting and Textures
CSCI4229 Summer 2016

Display multiple objects in 3D
Time to Complete: 12 hours
 
Key bindings
  
  a          Toggle axes
  0          Reset view angle
  1	     Toggle 1st Person mode ***Can only be done while already in Perspective***

  In 1st Person Mode:
  Up	     Moves camera forward 
  Left	     Rotates camera angle left
  Right      Rotates camera angle right
  Down	     Moves camera backward

  -	     Zoom in in Perspective mode
  +	     Zoom out in Perspective mode
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out  
  arrows     Change view angle (in Perspective Mode)

  l          Toggles lighting
  a/A        Decrease/increase ambient light
  d/D        Decrease/increase diffuse light
  s/S        Decrease/increase specular light
  e/E        Decrease/increase emitted light
  n/N        Decrease/increase shininess
  F3         Toggle light distance (1/5)
  m          Toggles light movement
  []         Lower/rise light
  x          Toggle axes
  ESC        Exit
